00:01:13.004 --> 00:01:16.084
OK then, Russian oligarchs in London.

00:01:17.714 --> 00:01:22.864
On July 1st of 2003 it was announced in the British press that a Russian

00:01:23.014 --> 00:01:28.054
called Roman Abramovich had bought Chelsea football club for £140 million.

00:01:29.254 --> 00:01:33.604
Not many Chelsea fans had heard of this man before, but they didn’t

